    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43556</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さっき、もらった絵って、
&lt;Arche&gt;さんが描いたんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That painting you just gave us... did you draw it, Miss &lt;Arche&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん、そーだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yup, that's right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え！？　あのヘンテコヘタクソな絵、
&lt;Arche&gt;さんが……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh!? This disgusting excuse of a sketch was drawn by Miss &lt;Arche&gt;...!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;！　そんなにはっきり言っちゃ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;! You shouldn't say things like that bluntly...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちっちっち、この絵のよさがわからないなんて
お子様だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, no, no. He can't see the merit in this painting as he's simply a snort.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもだもんな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I'm just a snort...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしはわかるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I think I do understand it, though!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, no...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>絵からほとばしる生命力や情熱を
いっぱい受け取って、背中がゾクゾクしました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This painting is filled with life and passion, it captures an amazing feeling and makes my bodytingle with excitement!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃん、大人♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;'s such a grown-up!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44400</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……よくわかんねや</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I don't really get it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_009_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ぼくもわからない……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I don't understand either...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
